# Agents — Backend

## Structure

```
backend/
├── agents/                        # Auto-discovered at startup
│   └── my_agent/
│       ├── agent.py               # Required: config + create_root_agent
│       └── tools/
│           ├── __init__.py
│           └── my_tool.py
│
└── src/api/
    ├── core/agents/               # Model registry, checkpointer, schemas
    ├── models/agents/             # SQLAlchemy: checkpoints + chat_history tables
    ├── repositories/agents/       # Chat history CRUD
    ├── services/agents/           # Registry, streaming, executors
    └── routes/agents/             # /chat/completions, /models, /threads
```

Directory name → model ID: `my_agent` → `"my-agent"` (underscores → hyphens).

